#: src/sphinx.md:49
msgid ""
"If you're using a mixed Rust/Python project layout, make sure you didn't add "
"the Python project path to `sys.path` in `conf.py` of Sphinx. Read The Docs "
"doesn't install your project in editable mode, adding it to `sys.path` will "
"make your project fail to import which breaks documentation generation."
msgstr ""

